title: Vondré - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG and Vive Latino present Live on KEXP from Mexico with Vondré performing at El Desierto Casa Estudio. Recorded March 16, 2023.

Songs:
Psicopatía
Lilith
No Me Impulses A Ser Así
Se Trata De Ti
Rotura

Ana Cristina Espinosa André - Vocals, Guitar
Elizabeth Olivarez - Guitar, Backing Vocals
Adrian Isaac Paz - Bass
Natalia Miranda Pavlovich - Drums, Backing Vocals

KEXP Live from Mexico: Vive Latino is a partnership with Vive Latino and Indie Rocks! Magazine

Recorded at El Desierto Casa Estudio in Desierto de Los Leones, Mexico

Host: Albina Cabrera
Videographers: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro & Scott Holpainen
Video Editor: Scott Holpainen
Audio Engineers: Daniel Bitran Arizpe, Julian Martlew, JC Vertii
Mixing & Mastering: Julian Martlew

Studio Manager: Gabriela Sandoval

Fixer: Danae Silva
